::: Megatron dosent even look at Deathcycle before he blasts him, along with 
the internal Auto-guns and other bots. :::

::: Megatron ::: Fool! Your not welcome here!

~~~~~~~~~~~~

::: Marine lays tired in bed, museing about how they will get off the 
rock. :::

::: Marine ::: How are we going to get away from here?

::: Ominous looks at him, and then walks towrds a wall made of thick ice. He 
pulls out a remote control to reveal a door. It slide opens and in the large 
chamber rests a Decepticon shuttle, under repairs. :::

::: Marine ::: What is that?!

::: Ominous ::: In a weeks time it will be our escape from here. We will load 
it with the energon, the Predacons who wish to leave, and go home.

::: Marine smiled. Finally good news. :::
